commit.message: Fix signature of catch_int

Allow a negative --elem-cnt-max. This will make the effective
elem-cnt-max depend on each password length. For example, using
--elem-cnt-max=-2 the effective max will be 3 at length 5, and
4 at length 6.

This makes it easier to eg. avoid candidates built from only
one-char elements.
